The Austria Taekwondo Federation is the largest Taekwondo Association in Austria. It is a member of the [[Austrian Olympic Committee]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619011008/http://www.oetdv.at/attachments/033_OTDV_Statuten_gv171214.pdf|title=Wayback Machine|date=19 June 2015|publisher=|accessdate=5 October 2018}}</ref>
==International competition==
Austria Taekwondo Federation is a member of the European umbrella organization [[European Taekwondo Union]] as well as the World Association for [[World Taekwondo]] (WT).
On the part of the Austria Olympic Committee, the Austria Taekwondo Federation is the only Taekwondo Association authorized to send athletes to the Olympic Games.
